longDescription:
PRODUCED BY TAO & SOUND (Custom audio)


Music Playlist


Music Generations 80's is a unique music pack, made for game developers who need 80’s-like realistic music loops for their videogames or for those devs who wish to enhance their games or apps with a rare yet elegant music touch.

Give your project that genuine 80’s style you are looking for! These loops are suitable for action, adventure or puzzle gameplay, in-game radio stations, main menus, credits scene, story scenes or background music for apps.


contact@taoandsound.com
technicalDetails:
Music Generations 80’s contains 8 original high quality music tracks and 12 additional background music files (e.g. bass and drums only or melody only) carefuly chosen to offer more versatility for the different scenes of your game.

Number of Audio tracks: 20
Number of Audio Cues: 20
Sample rate \ bit rate: 44.1 kHz, 16bit Stereo WAVs
Does music\audio loop: Yes
How many sound FX: no fx
How many minutes of audio provided: 21’40”
Engine Compatibility: Unreal 4.8.2
